text: Estes Brook is an unincorporated community in Mille Lacs County, Minnesota, United States. The community is located near the junction of Mille Lacs County Road 7 and 70th Street. County Road 13 is also in the immediate area. Estes Brook is located within Greenbush Township and Milo Township. Nearby places include Milaca, Foreston, and Princeton.Minnesota Place Names.
